                "text": " David A. Morrow, et. al. TIMI Risk Score for ST-Elevation Myocardial Infarction: A Convenient, Bedside, Clinical Score for Risk Assessment at Presentation: An Intravenous nPA for Treatment of Infarcting Myocardium Early II Trial Substudy Circulation. 2000; 102: 2031-2037 doi: 10.1161/01.CIR.102.17.2031"
